import axios, {
  AxiosRequestConfig,
  AxiosInstance,
  AxiosResponse,
  AxiosError,
} from "axios";

} from "./Models";

export interface ResponseDTO {
  code: number;
  data?: any;
  message?: string;
}

const init = (): AxiosInstance => {
  const api_url = "http://localhost/QTIMEWEB2/api";

  return axios.create({
    baseURL: api_url,
    timeout: 31000,
  });
};

export const getDataList = async (
  instance: AxiosInstance,
  url: string,
  params: AxiosRequestConfig | null = null
): Promise<ResponseDTO> => {
  const data = await instance
    .get(url, { ...(params && { params: params }) })
    .then((res: AxiosResponse) => {
      return {
        code: 200,
        data: res.data,
      };
    })
    .catch((err) => {
      return getErrorResponse(err);
    });

  return data;
};

const getErrorResponse = (error: AxiosError) => {
  if (error.response) {
    return {
      code: 400,
      data: error.response.data,
    };
  } else if (error.request) {
    return {
      code: 500,
      data: "Internal server error",
    };
  } else {
    return {
      code: 0,
      data: "Error in sending request",
    };
  }
};

export const getString = async (
  instance: AxiosInstance,
  url: string,
  params: AxiosRequestConfig | null = null
): Promise<ResponseDTO> => {
  const data = await instance
    .get(url, { ...(params && { params: params }) })
    .then((res) => {
      return {
        code: 200,
        data: res.data,
      };
    })
    .catch((err) => {
      return getErrorResponse(err);
    });

  return data;
};

export const sendData = async (
  instance: AxiosInstance,
  url: string,
  params: AxiosRequestConfig | null = null
): Promise<ResponseDTO> => {
  const data = await instance
    .post(url, { ...params })
    .then((res) => {
      return {
        code: 200,
        data: res.data,
      };
    })
    .catch((err) => {
      return getErrorResponse(err);
    });

  return data;
};

export const Api = {
  getSession: async (username: string, password: string): Promise<any> => {
    // return new Promise(resolve => setTimeout(resolve, 1000, "A9F9E99E-2B73-43D3-B76E-4CBBFC0CE37F"));
    return await getString(init(), `/Sessions/${username}/${password}`);
  },
};
